        <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title">User Search</h4>
            <p class="card-text">Easily search for GitHub users with a responsive input box. View the top results in an intuitive list of user cards.</p>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="card1 card text-start">
       
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title">User Repository Table</h4>
            <p class="card-text">Click on a user to navigate to a detailed page showcasing their repositories. View essential information including the repository name, description, stars, forks, and open issue.</p>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="card1 card text-start">
       
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title">Sorting Options</h4>
